name: starwars_xx trading cards #19: Father Fett
description:
This Father don’t come with no wine and crackers.

Is he directing incoming flights? Do they have the same rules for jet packs? Is there an FAA on Mandalore and if so, is it controlled by the church? On account of beings moving around the heavens and whatnot.

Alright, alright, I’m totally kidding, he’s got a fanny pack full of wine and lord crisps under that frock. Among other surprises…
